Package hu.bme.mit.theta.xsts.dsl.gen

Class XstsDslBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.bme.mit.theta.xsts.dsl.gen.XstsDslBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    XstsDslListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    public class XstsDslBaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements XstsDslListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of XstsDslListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
